    kw_rev:['arrogance', 'impulsiveness', 'forceful', 'domineering'],
    up:'The King of Wands is a master of vision and inspired leadership. He acts boldly, leads by example and brings others along through sheer charisma and competence. Take the lead — others will follow.',
