    kw_rev:['restlessness', 'burnout', 'inability to rest', 're-awakening'],
    up:'The Four of Swords commands you to stop and rest. Your mind and body need recovery time before the next challenge. This is not defeat — it is the wisdom to know that action without rest leads to collapse.',
